PrecisAppointment of Kenneth Alvin Johnstone, of Red Deer, Alberta, as a member of the Canadian Dairy Commission to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective June 1, 1994, in the place of Frank A. Claydon, whose term has expired.
